/p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742993-catalyst-pharma-agamree-is-its-key-to-a-sustainable-future", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:40:18"}, {"id": "4742854", "title": "2 Solid Yields From Preferred Stocks For Uncertain Times", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red squirrel fills up its shopping trolley full of hazelnuts.\" data-id=\"1443871198\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">AGD Beukhof/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-authored with Hidden Opportunities</em></p> <p>Winter is here. The air is crisp, and depending on where you live, the first snow may already be blanketing the ground. Nature instinctively prepares for the season; trees shed their leaves, squirrels hoard nuts, and bears</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742854-2-solid-yields-from-preferred-stocks-for-uncertain-times", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:35:00"}]}